metadata.name: Untitled 1/1
metadata.description:
At odds with digital cash protocols. Good metaphors for visual synthetic semantics. Control of keys, provable removals, operational callbacks. Machines unstoppable, doing 75 down the freeway. Wide black velvet choker, ruched corset top pair. Chunky ruthenium digicore collar necklace. 

Synth Graph: high resolution full body photograph of a beautiful pink haired tanned supermodel posing with luxury fashion streetwear, wearing a black choker necklace, captured with a Nikon D7100, high resolution, 8k, very detailed, highly realistic. Sampler: plms, steps: 70, scale: 10.
